videos.description: K.J. Walton intercepts pass and throws it down on the other end for Mizzou.
videos.headline: Walton throws it down for Mizzou

videos.description: Jordan Barnett gets a block before punishing the rim at the other end.
videos.headline: Barnett punishes the rim

videos.description: Jordan Barnett finds Russell Woods inside for a the dunk.
videos.headline: Russell Woods rocks the rim

videos.description: Reed Nikko dunks it down after Terrence Phillips finds him open inside.
videos.headline: Phillips finds Nikko with a sweet dish for the dunk

videos.description: Bam Adebayo throws down the putback dunk off a miss from Malik Monk.
videos.headline: Adebayo throws down the putback dunk with authority

videos.description: K.J. Walton scores a tough layup on Bam Adebayo as Mizzou tries to keep it close.
videos.headline: Walton kisses it high off the glass as he scores on Adebayo

videos.description: Bam Adebayo throws down another dunk as Mizzou struggles to stop him.
videos.headline: Adebayo continues his dominance inside with another dunk

videos.description: Josh Barnett doing his best to keep Mizzou alive as he blows by Wenyen Gabriel for the dunk.
videos.headline: Barnett blows by Gabriel for the two-handed slam

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox finds Derek Willis for the alley-oop. Is that the dagger for Mizzou?
videos.headline: Willis catches the lob and throws it down
